Ma tiṭ-ik d ṭṭlam, tafat ad k-teɛmu.
Win yebɣan, yeqqar amek ; win ur nebɣi, yeqqar ulamek.
Ad neddu, ad neddu, alamma yeɣli udabu.
D aksar, d asawen, izukar d imeksawen.
Iḍarren-is deg ubellaɛ, yettmami ddellaɛ.
Zeggiren at nnif, rennu-d at lḥif, ineggura ṭṭafaren-d bessif.
Nnig ubrid, ddaw ubrid, leqrar-is d abrid.
Ttwaliɣ ayen s i umneɣ.
Iswi-nneɣ d tilelli s wudmawen akk i tesɛa.
Bdiɣ ferrẓeɣ timsal.
Ad k-id-ḥellqent,ma d nekk i d ameɛfun !
